The paper deals with the problem of finding periodicity in a data stream, which is a fundamental problem in data structures (cs.DS) and computational complexity (cs.CC). The use of mismatches in the definition of periodicity suggests a connection to combinatorics (cs.DM) and information theory (cs.IT). Finally, the use of streaming algorithms and space complexity suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG).
